title: Rand Paul Autographs Hillary Clinton’s Book, Resells It As Fiction
text: Rand Paul has received an autographed copy of Hillary Clinton’s book, Hard Choices. The Republican presidential hopeful placed it for resale on eBay — but not before adding his own autograph. As a final insult, in the auction description Paul labeled the book as “fiction.” It appears that Hillary Clinton’s campaign sent Rand Paul, along...
